{"tid":1485581,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"而家係2005年，大家好，我係來自14年後嘅未來人","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T18:19:40.000Z","uid":165817,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"16bd59a9dd0afe29353512119805b6b6dd163c27","tid":1485581,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"而家嘅球壇百花齊放，除咗老化緊嘅施丹同朗拿度之外，英超嘅亨利同雙特、西甲嘅細哨同迪高、意甲嘅舒夫真高同阿祖安奴，都有力爭世一之長短。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個格局，好快就會改寫。喺幾年之後，有兩位年青球員會開始爆發，佢地兩個會瓜分壟斷連續十年歐洲足球先生，仲會合共攞咗15個聯賽同9個歐聯冠軍，亦都會進步成為歷史上其中兩個最高成就嘅足球員。<br />\n<br />\n而家嘅新星真係好多，一代新人隨時勝舊人。我而家要趕住返去2019，2005年嘅球迷們，你地又覺得，呢兩個即將爆發嘅小將，會係邊兩個呢? 係神童朗尼? 第N個新肥馬美斯? 定係電單車雷耶斯?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Q9uSZG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Q9uSZG.jpg&h=df4b7b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KG8rVc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKG8rVc3.jpg&h=f50c5b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3Qh1S3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3Qh1S3.jpg&h=bc5e397f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ZAmJ6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ZAmJ6p.jpg&h=7d1a758c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHk6aMq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHk6aMq.jpg&h=e0298fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBirVc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBirVc5.jpg&h=f07369d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzVqrjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzVqrjG.jpg&h=1a71b6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nBMQCrr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMQCrr.jpg&h=9d783f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AD